GSD.description:
perf/x86/intel/uncore: Fix reference count leak in __uncore_imc_init_box()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.86 by commit 0358bc7cc21ad972a06918f3cf2222dc40127cb8, it was introduced in version v5.7 by commit fdb64822443ec9fb8c3a74b598a74790ae8d2e22. For more details please see the references link.
